==English==

===Etymology===
From Greek [[ἀγλαϊα]] (aglaia), meaning '[[resplandor, belleza, la resplandeciente]]'. The youngest of the three Graces, daughter of eus and Eurynome. Spouse of Hefestus.

===Proper noun===
'''Aglaia'''

#{{given name|female|}} A female [[given name]].

